oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Flatt and Scruggs at Nancy Aud.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Flatt and Scruggs and the Foggy Mountain Boys (Musical group); Flatt, Lester; Scruggs, Earl; Martha White Foods; Grand Ole Opry (radio program); Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and blue on white) announcing WSM Grand Ole Opry stars Lester Flatt and Earl Scruggs with the Foggy Mountain Boys at the Nancy Auditorium on November 19. Poster features metal photoplates of Earl Scruggs and Lester Flatt.
